00:14:06.970 --> 00:14:09.130
<font color="#ffffff">oder von Migros, Coop, Denner,</font>

279
00:14:09.290 --> 00:14:13.130
<font color="#ffffff">Lastwagen, die unseren Binnenmarkt</font>
